"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-tv-lifestyle-paris-bistros-olympics-waiters-race-b2518227.html\", \"text\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  00:52  Oliver Browning|Monday 25 March 2024 14:55GMT  Atraditiondating back to 1914 has been revived inParisas the French capital prepares to welcome theOlympic Gamesthis summer.  Thewaiter's race - open to thestaffof all Parisian bistros - was organised in front of the Paristown hallon Sunday 24 March.  Dozens of participants set off carrying a plate with a croissant,coffeeand a glass ofwaterfor a 1.2 mile-long route through the Marais neighborhood in central Paris.  An essential element of Parisian heritage, bistros are at the heart of the effort to promote the Parisian way of life and attract visitors during the Olympics.  04:10  02:59  00:50  01:20  05:16  09:16  40:26  06:56  07:03  05:30  05:37  45:14  14:11  12:18  30:24  16:08  17:41  18:22  13:43  12:41  41:50  48:45  40:57  37:44  56:37  58:53  41:30  56:09  07:11  08:32  05:45  05:35  08:02  06:42  05:23  07:08  07:40  08:56  13:49  10:57  07:53  19:31  04:07  11:19  02:50  Sponsored  03:09  Sponsored  02:39  Sponsored  01:53  Sponsored  01:39  Sponsored  02:40  Sponsored  07:30  07:54  05:23  05:35  09:47  06:28  06:23  07:35  08:03  11:54  08:21  06:38  07:25  04:31  07:30  03:34  13:23  17:05  03:51  04:18  06:26  04:30  03:35  03:45  02:03  03:22  02:15  02:22  02:21  01:43  01:42  01:45  10:44  03:44  07:42  09:22  06:11  07:50  06:21  02:19  10:42  06:27  07:23  06:35  12:18  11:50  09:03  13:07  02:10  00:45  01:05  00:42  00:36  00:33  00:35  00:57  00:14  03:03  00:21  01:10  00:20  00:57  00:17  00:31  00:49  00:33  01:00  00:31  00:54  01:08  01:35  00:47  01:19  02:33  00:23  00:22  00:59  01:23  00:28  00:27  03:29  03:07  03:07  03:24  01:36  00:42  01:26  00:32  00:31  02:00  00:40  00:58  04:23